					an open-source license, source code or license text is provided on that page or on
					written request to
					<a href={mailtoHref('legal')} class="text-fuchsia-300 underline hover:text-fuchsia-200">{EMAILS.legal}</a>.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">1.7 User-provided content</h2>
				<p class="mt-3">
					The Software is a media player and recorder. You are solely responsible for the content
					you load, play, capture, record, screenshot, or otherwise process with the Software,
					including ensuring that you have all necessary rights, licenses, and permissions for
