					service of any third-party platform involved. See the
					<a href={LEGAL_ROUTES.acceptableUse} class="text-fuchsia-300 underline hover:text-fuchsia-200">Acceptable Use Policy</a>.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">1.8 Disclaimer of warranties</h2>
				<p class="mt-3 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-200">
					The Software is provided "as is" and "as available," without warranty of any kind,
					express, implied, or statutory, including but not limited to implied warranties of
					merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, title, and non-infringement.
