					supersedes all prior agreements. Ultiplay may modify this Agreement by posting an updated
					version at <a href="/" class="text-fuchsia-300 underline hover:text-fuchsia-200">ultiplay.net</a>;
					your continued use of the Software after the updated effective date constitutes
					acceptance. Material changes will be highlighted in the document-history table on the
					<a href={LEGAL_ROUTES.index} class="text-fuchsia-300 underline hover:text-fuchsia-200">legal index</a>.
